# Technical Stack: Safety Road Backend

## Core Framework
- **Language**: Java 17 (LTS)
- **Framework**: Spring Boot 3.x
- **Build Tool**: Gradle 8.x (Groovy DSL)

## Database & Storage
- **RDBMS**: MySQL 8.x (InnoDB, utf8mb4)
- **ORM**: Spring Data JPA (Hibernate)
- **Migration**: Flyway (Recommended for schema management)
- **Storage**: AWS S3 (Image files)

## Security
- **Authentication**: Spring Security 6.x + JWT
- **Encryption**: BCrypt for passwords

## API Documentation
- **Spec**: OpenAPI 3.0
- **Tool**: Swagger UI (Springdoc OpenAPI)

## Testing
- **Unit Test**: JUnit 5, Mockito
- **Integration Test**: @SpringBootTest
- **API Test**: Postman / Swagger

## Infrastructure (Dev/Prod)
- **Cloud**: AWS (EC2/ECS, RDS)
- **CI/CD**: GitHub Actions (Planned)
- **AI Integration**: Python Bridge (REST API Call)
